{"created": "2026-03-25T12:21:35.474839", "current_version": "1.0.0", "project": "ESP32 Distance Sensor", "versions": {"1.0.0": {"created": "2026-03-25T12:21:35.474837", "creator": {"program": "sphinx_needs", "version": "8.0.0"}, "needs": {"SPEC_LED_API_2": {"acceptance_criteria": "", "api_signature": "", "arch": {}, "avatar": null, "closed_at": null, "completion": null, "component": "", "constraints": [], "constraints_error": null, "constraints_passed": true, "constraints_results": {}, "content": "**Design:** Efficient batch operations for common patterns and hardware updates.\n\n**Implementation:**\n\n- ``led_clear_all()``: Set all LEDs to off state in single operation\n- ``led_show()``: Transmit complete buffer to hardware via RMT (enables REQ_LED_4)\n- Color Utilities: ``led_color_rgb()`` constructor, ``led_color_brightness()`` scaling\n- Status Functions: ``led_get_count()``, ``led_is_initialized()`` for state queries\n- Atomic Updates: Buffer modifications independent until ``led_show()`` called\n\n**Validation:** Clear all zeros entire buffer, show triggers RMT transmission, utilities\nproduce correct colors.", "created_at": null, "docname": "12_design/spec_led_controller", "doctype": ".rst", "duration": null, "external_css": "external_link", "external_url": null, "has_dead_links": false, "has_forbidden_dead_links": false, "header_file": "", "id": "SPEC_LED_API_2", "id_prefix": null, "is_external": false, "is_import": false, "is_modified": false, "jinja_content": false, "layout": null, "lineno": 80, "links": ["REQ_LED_2", "REQ_LED_4"], "links_back": [], "max_amount": null, "max_content_lines": null, "modifications": 0, "parameters": "", "params": null, "parent_need": null, "parent_needs": [], "parent_needs_back": [], "parts": {}, "post_content": null, "post_template": null, "pre_content": null, "pre_template": null, "prefix": null, "priority": "", "query": null, "rationale": "", "returns": "", "section_name": "API Specifications", "sections": ["API Specifications", "LED Controller Design Specification"], "service": null, "signature": null, "specific": null, "status": "approved", "style": null, "tags": ["led", "api", "batch"], "template": null, "title": "Batch Operations API", "type": "spec", "type_name": "Design Specification", "updated_at": null, "url": null, "url_postfix": null, "user": null}}, "needs_amount": 1}}}